    <string name="about_text">Trip Companion\n\nAdd the \"POI Catalog\" data field to any ride page — it adapts to its slot, so a small one on the map page works as a next-POI glance and a full-page one as the catalog.\n\nEverything works offline — 79 POIs and photos are bundled.\n\nRoute: Břeclav → Velehrad → Otrokovice.</string>

